Author: SHossain#0007
Content:
jl777 implemented `-ac_adaptivepow` 2 days ago https://medium.com/@jameslee777/adaptivepow-the-solution-to-diff-stranding-of-smaller-blockchains-425609df5563
We are testing high hashrate attack on Komodo assetchains in #talk-mining channel. This hashrate attack will run for 30 mins max and diff will be very high. Then, we will stop all ASIC mining and use only 1 CPU thread to continue mining which will bring the diff down and the chain will not be stranded. This test will start at 8PM UTC today which is about 5 mis away.
You can keep an eye on the stats here http://178.159.11.114:8080/stats
If you want to help and have ASIC or hashpower, please point at stratum+tcp://178.159.11.114:3033
